{"id":"63f85b5db6726b001b2b1e44","title":"Proxmox の VM に xterm.js でアクセスする","image":null,"created":1677220701,"updated":1677220705,"lines":[{"id":"63f85b5db6726b001b2b1e44","text":"Proxmox の VM に xterm.js でアクセスする","created":1677220701,"updated":1677220701},{"id":"63f85b5d4ade4d0000d94572","text":"from [20230223] #0223","created":1677220701,"updated":1677220705},{"id":"63f85b5d4ade4d0000d94573","text":"[Proxmox] の VM に [xterm.js] でアクセスする","created":1677220701,"updated":1677220701},{"id":"63f85b5d4ade4d0000d94574","text":"\t[noVNC] だとコピペができなくて不便ということに気付いた","created":1677220701,"updated":1677220701},{"id":"63f85b5d4ade4d0000d94575","text":"\t\t他には [SPICE] ってやつもコンソールで使えるっぽいが、xterm.js 使えるならそれが手っ取り早そうだなと","created":1677220701,"updated":1677220701},{"id":"63f85b5d4ade4d0000d94576","text":"\tハードウェアの Add からシリアルポートを追加する","created":1677220701,"updated":1677220701},{"id":"63f85b5d4ade4d0000d94577","text":"\t\tとりあえず `serial0`","created":1677220701,"updated":1677220701},{"id":"63f85b5d4ade4d0000d94578","text":"\tそしたら noVNC で一旦入って、`sudo systemctl enable serial-getty@ttyS0.service`, `sudo systemctl start serial-getty@ttyS0.service` てな感じで仮想シリアルポートを有効化しないといけないみたい","created":1677220701,"updated":1677220701},{"id":"63f85b5d4ade4d0000d94579","text":"\tするとコンソールから xterm.js で接続できた","created":1677220701,"updated":1677220701},{"id":"63f85b5d4ade4d0000d9457a","text":"","created":1677220701,"updated":1677220701}]}